---
title: "Offline | Stödlinjer Sverige"
description: "Viktiga stödnummer att ha sparade när du är offline."
permalink: "/offline/"
noindex: true
pageClass: "solid-bg-shell offline-page"
header:
  icon: "life-ring"
  label: "Offline"
  title: "Stödlinjer Sverige"
  subtitle: "Viktiga nummer när nätet saknas"
  links:
    - url: "/"
      icon: "home"
      text: "Start"
      aria: "Till startsidan"
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}
{% from "partials/icon.njk" import icon %}

{% block header %}
  {% include "partials/header.njk" %}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="offline-section max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <div class="surface-card strong-card offline-card p-6 sm:p-8">
      <span class="pill mb-4">{{ icon('web') }} Offline</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
        Viktiga nummer
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg muted mb-6">
        Du verkar vara offline. Här är viktiga nummer som kan vara bra att ha sparade.
      </p>

      <div class="offline-number-list">
        <a href="tel:112" class="offline-number-link" aria-label="Ring SOS Alarm 112">
          <span>
            <strong>SOS Alarm</strong>
            <span>Akut fara</span>
          </span>
          <span class="phone-number">112</span>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:90101" class="offline-number-link" aria-label="Ring Självmordslinjen 90101">
          <span>
            <strong>Självmordslinjen</strong>
            <span>Samtal och stöd</span>
          </span>
          <span class="phone-number">90101</span>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:020505050" class="offline-number-link" aria-label="Ring Kvinnofridslinjen 020-50 50 50">
          <span>
            <strong>Kvinnofridslinjen</strong>
            <span>Våld och hot</span>
          </span>
          <span class="phone-number">020-50 50 50</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
